author: rgardler
msg: Set wookie domain, port and path in the build.properties so that they can be overridden in local.build.properties.
This allows the scratchpad/admin-ui to be tested in environments where we are not running at the standard location.

Also add run args for running in developer mode to the build.properties. This was already functional and documented, but it is handy to have an example of it in the properties file so that people see it is available (not everyone reads docs)
